---
import Section from '../common/Section.astro';
---

<Section background="gray" id="values">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Our Principles</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Guiding values for every tool we build.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
    <!-- Value 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1a1a24] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Privacy as Sanctuary</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Your spiritual life is between you and God.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Value 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1a1a24] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Freely Given</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        "Freely you have received; freely give." No cost, no ads, just a gift to the Church.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Value 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1a1a24] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"></line><line x1="2" y1="7" x2="22" y2="7"></line></svg> <!-- Placeholder for Cross -->
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Faithful</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Rooted in Sacred Scripture, Tradition, and the Magisterium of the Catholic Church.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Value 4 -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1a1a24] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-2.246-5.318-2.5-7-1.5 6-3 8-3 8q1 1 2 2.5c1 1.5 2 2.5 2 2.5z"/><path d="M15.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 13 12c0-1.38.5-2 1-3 1.072-2.143 2.246-5.318 2.5-7 1.5 6 3 8 3 8q-1 1-2 2.5c-1 1.5-2 2.5-2 2.5z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Excellence</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        "Do it all for the glory of God." Professional quality, worthy of serving the faithful.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Value 5 -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1a1a24] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Open Source</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Transparency builds trust. All our apps are open source — view, audit, and contribute on GitHub.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
